that produce different patterns on Picbreeder.  To address this
question, P=
icbreeder now displays the number of nodes and number of
connections in eve=
ry published CPPN on the site.  The detailed display
of any image (i.e. whe=
n you click on images that are in lists) shows
information right above the =
enlarged image.
